notes:
[Eldrazi Skyspawner] is the pick here as it's probably the best common.

[Brutal Expulsion] while it's one of those cards that certain people are really going to love, isn't really good enough to go into two colours for, even if they are good colours in the format.

The runner up is probably [Evolving Wilds] which is kind of sad, but other than the Skyspawner this pack it pretty disappointing.
